com.hp.autonomy.aci.content.printfields

Class PrintFields

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.autonomy.aci.content.printfields.PrintFields
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>

    public class PrintFields
extends Object
implements Iterable<String>
    Helper class for building printfields, such as those used in the printfields parameter of a query. Individual field names are represented as Strings and deduplicated where possible in a case-sensitive manner. No attempt is currently made to interpret wildcards intelligently.

    This class makes no attempt at internal synchronization and is not safe to be used by multiple threads without external synchronization.
